{"tid":877571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【高層跌到420萬】兩個月前5球買金獅花園樓王 即輸兩成","createTime":"2018-10-26T12:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T23:36:51.000Z","uid":75877,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"79800da292945687c0908c59d308800f9a861cce","tid":877571,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"樓價下跌真的很可怕，細價樓跌幅竟然可能兩個月跌兩成。世紀21奇豐王兆昌表示，新近錄得大圍金獅花園1期成交，單位為F座 金豐閣高層05室，實用面積266方呎，以420萬元易手，呎價15,789元。據資料，同座樓下中層3室，實用面積較細，得260方呎，今年8月以510萬元沽出，呎價19,615元破盡屋苑紀錄，是次成交短短兩個月劈價19.5%，賣平90萬元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主早1987年5月購入上址，當時作價23.9萬元，持貨至今轉售，賬面獲利396.1萬元，31年多升值16倍。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰"},{"pid":"b97a0373125802ded925d3b748a1691eb6b362f7","tid":877571,"uid":35941,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"高層平中層100萬有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b390eb82072e195da131eec527ebf1b446b7f3","tid":877571,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b97a0373125802ded925d3b748a1691eb6b362f7","tid":877571,"uid":35941,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"高層平中層100萬有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"座向唔同 無得咁計"},{"pid":"11d876c2229bca1bf6fc514a26f464ae4853da40","tid":877571,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b97a0373125802ded925d3b748a1691eb6b362f7","tid":877571,"uid":35941,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"高層平中層100萬有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"agger   高層水壓好低   屎都沖唔乾淨"},{"pid":"fb6dd3a73deaefe79b178cd054e5a90157977a5a","tid":877571,"uid":7369,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"11d876c2229bca1bf6fc514a26f464ae4853da40","tid":877571,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote